1
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,359
It's on you.

2
00:01:18,999 --> 00:01:19,880
Are you sure?

3
00:01:19,999 --> 00:01:20,600
I'm not.

4
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,040
But I'll

5
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:23,199
give it a try.

6
00:01:28,119 --> 00:01:29,320
Don't worry.

7
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,839
I'm good at slicing meat.

8
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,359
I've sliced the meat of sheep

9
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,800
we ate after every victory

10
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,399
in the army, whether it was

11
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:38,359
grilled or boiled.

12
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:39,759
I won't

13
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:41,320
make you suffer.

14
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,759
So you treat me like an animal?

15
00:01:45,199 --> 00:01:45,759
I refuse.

16
00:01:53,199 --> 00:01:54,399
Have you thought of a way yet?

17
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,839
Shh.

18
00:01:55,999 --> 00:01:56,880
I'm thinking.

19
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,120
Why is there no reaction?

20
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,880
What's wrong?

21
00:02:48,239 --> 00:02:49,519
There is no other way now.

22
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,400
Only cooperation can win.

23
00:02:51,799 --> 00:02:53,199
How about making a deal?

24
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,280
Must...

25
00:02:59,679 --> 00:03:00,479
Must be like this?

26
00:03:01,079 --> 00:03:01,440
Yes.

27
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,239
We can swear an oath

28
00:03:03,359 --> 00:03:04,440
with blood.

29
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,720
That's fine.

30
00:03:07,239 --> 00:03:08,840
But before we get the Star Tokens,

31
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,320
you must follow my instructions.

32
00:03:10,679 --> 00:03:11,519
Report to me

33
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,160
wherever you go,

34
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,519
whoever you meet,

35
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:16,600
and whatever you do,

36
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,639
including leaving.

37
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,639
You're my prisoner.

38
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,880
Stop talking.

39
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,280
As the container of the Star Tokens,

40
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,880
you must protect it well.

41
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,799
You can't let it suffer any damage.

42
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,120
Until

43
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,079
it returns to the Star Chart of Qixi.

44
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:42,479
Right.

45
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,120
That's why I let you lose so much blood.

46
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,479
You dare to send me?

47
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,799
You're the first one.

48
00:04:02,519 --> 00:04:03,000
Yes.

49
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,160
What?

50
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,199
You want to go back on your word?

51
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,760
What are you doing?

52
00:04:39,119 --> 00:04:40,119
Guardian Star Symbol.

53
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,640
This is my home.

54
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,679
I'm not going anywhere.

55
00:04:42,679 --> 00:04:44,559
What kind of Star Symbol are you guarding?

56
00:04:44,559 --> 00:04:46,760
Didn't you tell me to stay by your side?

57
00:04:46,999 --> 00:04:48,520
But before the Star Symbol is retrieved,

58
00:04:48,799 --> 00:04:50,319
you must follow my arrangements.

59
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,919
You must report to me wherever you go or whom you meet.

60
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,040
Stay by my side and follow my orders.

61
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,679
That's right.

62
00:04:58,160 --> 00:05:00,799
But it's four in the morning.

63
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:03,439
I finish my morning exercise at 3:00 AM every day.

64
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,040
That's in the novel.

65
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,799
This is the real world.

66
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,999
If you're really that bored,

67
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,999
then go make breakfast.

68
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,919
I'll get up.

69
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:24,520
I'll get up, okay?

70
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,479
Hey.

71
00:05:25,919 --> 00:05:26,600
Where are you going?

72
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:27,640
I'm going

73
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:28,720
to the bathroom.

74
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,720
Do you still want to follow me?

75
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:30,319
Yeah.

76
00:05:30,559 --> 00:05:31,280
If you need me.

77
00:05:31,999 --> 00:05:32,840
Just treat me

78
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,479
I didn't say anything.

79
00:05:35,479 --> 00:05:35,760
Ah.

80
00:05:46,559 --> 00:05:46,960
Have a taste.

81
00:05:48,999 --> 00:05:50,160
Come out!

82
00:05:50,559 --> 00:05:52,319
You're not allowed to enter the kitchen.

83
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,400
Why don't you question my background?

84
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:15,040
This thing clearly appeared on me.

85
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,280
Even if you say you knew me before,

86
00:06:21,559 --> 00:06:22,600
I wouldn't find it strange.

87
00:06:32,999 --> 00:06:33,600
Hmm.

88
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:41,239
You also have the habit of adding sugar to porridge.

89
00:06:41,799 --> 00:06:42,160
Why?

90
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,439
Now you want to get close to me?

91
00:06:49,999 --> 00:06:50,280
Yes.

92
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,359
What are you doing?

93
00:07:02,919 --> 00:07:03,359
Brushing teeth.

94
00:07:07,119 --> 00:07:07,799
No need.

95
00:07:08,119 --> 00:07:09,999
I've already brushed my teeth this morning.

96
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,439
You just ate so much sugar.

97
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:14,479
Come on.

98
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:15,520
Let me help you.

99
00:07:20,119 --> 00:07:20,520
It's okay.

100
00:07:20,799 --> 00:07:21,559
This thing won't hurt you.

101
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,080
Open your mouth.

102
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:29,879
Open it wider.

103
00:07:57,799 --> 00:07:58,760
Don't waste time.

104
00:07:58,999 --> 00:07:59,960
I'll do it myself.

105
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:06,640
Can we go now?

106
00:08:16,119 --> 00:08:16,600
Wear this.

107
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:24,679
This one.

108
00:08:24,799 --> 00:08:25,479
Wear it inside.

109
00:08:28,479 --> 00:08:29,559
What is this?

110
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,960
A chest guard?

111
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,160
The quality isn't good.

112
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,280
It's too thin.

113
00:08:34,599 --> 00:08:36,160
It can't block blades or swords.

114
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,079
How do I wear it?

115
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,799
Is there a possibility that it's just

116
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,360
not a chest guard?

117
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,839
Then what is it?

118
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:44,240
No, this...
